attributes.additional_details:
The country is going backwards in dental care.
We are going to have a generation who have bad teeth and will need dentures.
Private dental care is unaffordable for millions of people and the government needs to get the situation resolved.
attributes.background: I want every child to be able to see an NHS dentist and for the government to find dentists to be able to start taking on NHS patients.

rejection.details: You may wish to sign this petition which calls for a similar action: https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/625518
